Prerequisites for installation
------------------------------

* Required

- OCaml (http://caml.inria.fr/)
- ocamlgraph (http://ocamlgraph.lri.fr/)

* Optional

- For graphical interface
. LablGTK2 (http://wwwfun.kurims.kyoto-u.ac.jp/soft/lsl/lablgtk.html)
  with GLADE (http://www.jamesh.id.au/software/libglade/)
  and GTKGLArea (http://www.mono-project.com/GtkGLArea)
  support
. LablGL (http://wwwfun.kurims.kyoto-u.ac.jp/soft/lsl/lablgl.html)

- For additional computation features
. Numerix (http://pauillac.inria.fr/~quercia/)


* On Debian systems, the corresponding packages can be installed by typing

apt-get install ocaml libocamlgraph-ocaml-dev liblablgtk2-ocaml-dev liblablgtk2-gl-ocaml-dev liblablgl-ocaml-dev


Installing
----------
Typing

./configure
make
make install

will be enough.
